      <div class="msgContentFrame">@Rinsui <br /><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Quote:</div><div class="orig">When mages boss people around to stand in the line of fire something is broken.</div></div> <br /> <br />I agree. That being said, I was doing efts today with a party that was quite good. <br />For those of you who don't know, Efts have a direction AoE lightning attack that can do 600+ damage through shell. <br /> <br />Now there was 1 tank, and he was quite good at holding hate. He was using provoke, taunt and second wind. <br />Only when we took adds on accident was there really a need for AoE heals at all. Even by spamming spirit dart, and trying to debuff, I was getting 50-100 sp per fight, all the archers and melees were claiming they were getting 300-400. <br /> <br />That hardly seems fair, either. We don't get SP for healing ourselves, and the one person who was taking a little damage was also using second wind? To my knowledge he's not going to get any SP from that, ever, while he's stealing what little SP i could get from healing him. <br /> <br />I understand that if you wanted to be a tank, you'd have made a tank. But If you want me to help you, then jesus, you should want to help me too. That's the defnition of teamwork.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV: Taiga Halak, Fabul <br /> <br />FFXI: Talina, Valefor (retired)</div></div>
